reviewText:
I had fond memories of the first Sniper Elite.
Now, after playing a few levels from this game, I've noticed a few things:
- You are not meant to be stealthy, you will have to slaughter most enemies in each level;
- Sound design is ♥♥♥♥ poor for weapons, the silenced pistol makes as much noise as the sniper rifle; all guns are so pew pew" that you will have a hard time finding out where you get shot from;
- The enemy AI is pretty bad
